Enhancing the Project with MongoDB for Scalable Storage and Analysis
To scale our Russian troop movement prediction system, weâ€™ll integrate MongoDB as our database. This allows us to efficiently store, retrieve, and query geospatial data, timelines, and model predictions while handling real-time updates.

1. Setting Up MongoDB for Troop Movement Tracking
Installation (If Needed)
If you havenâ€™t installed MongoDB yet, you can do so using:

bash
Copy
Edit
